    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="class_swatch" kindref="compound">Swatch</ref> class is a thin wrapper around the KisSwatch class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A <ref refid="class_swatch" kindref="compound">Swatch</ref> is a single color that is part of a palette, that has a name and an id. A <ref refid="class_swatch" kindref="compound">Swatch</ref> color can be a spot color. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
